Package: file-guard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, fuse3, libfuse3-3
Description: Per-process credential access control daemon
 file-guard enforces per-process allow/deny policy for sensitive
 credential files and serves authorized accesses through a FUSE mount.
